sentences: THE ELEV3N is an American producer, songwriter, and multi-instrumentalist team currently based in New York City.

Since forming in 2011, the trio has achieved success in production and songwriting for pop, hip hop and R&B acts such as Meghan Trainor, Karmin, Sean Kingston, Cher Lloyd, Jesse McCartney, Bea Miller and The Wanted.

After reconnecting with former Berklee classmate and friend  Nils Gums of The Complex Group in 2012 the team entered into a management agreement with the Complex Group and landed a production deal with Antonio L.A.
